alks%20between%20two%20countries.%20The%20death%20of%20Prakriti%20Lamsal%2C%20a%2020-year-old%20Nepalese%20student%20at%20Kalinga%20Institute%20of%20Industrial%20Technology%20(KIIT)%20in%20Bhubaneswar%20set%20off%20a%20storm%20of%20allegations%2C%20arrests%2C%20diplomatic%20unease%2C%20and%20student%20unrest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happened%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakriti%2C%20a%20third-year%20B.Tech%20(Computer%20Science)%20student%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20her%20hostel%20room%20on%20Sunday%20afternoon.%20The%20police%20initially%20registered%20it%20as%20a%20case%20of%20suicide%2C%20but%20the%20circumstances%20surrounding%20her%20death%20triggered%20protests%20within%20the%20campus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20from%20Nepal%20demanded%20an%20inquiry%20and%20accountability%20from%20the%20university%20administration%20whom%20they%20accuse%20of%20ignoring%20Prakriti's%20requests%20for%20intervention.%20Prakriti%20was%20allegedly%20being%20subjected%20to%20both%20physical%20and%20verbal%20abuse%20by%20Advik%20Shrivastava%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20BTech%20(Mechanical)%20student%20of%20the%20same%20university.%20In%20an%20audio%20file%2C%20which%20went%20viral%20after%20Prakriti's%20body%20was%20discovered%2C%20a%20man%20can%20be%20heard%20unleashing%20an%20expletives-ridden%20tirade%20against%20a%20woman%20who%20can%20be%20heard%20sobbing.%20The%20man%20forces%20the%20woman%20to%20call%20herself%20a%20%26quot%3Bwh*r*%26quot%3B%20and%20even%20manipulates%20an%20apology%20out%20of%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audio%20features%20both%20individuals%20addressing%20each%20other%20as%20Advik%20and%20Prakriti%2C%20however%2C%20NDTV%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20the%20clip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvik%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Lucknow%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20Monday%20from%20outside%20Bhubaneswar's%20airport%20and%20charged%20with%20abetment%20of%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakriti's%20body%2C%20after%20a%20post-mortem%20at%20AIIMS%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20her%20family.%20It%20will%20be%20flown%20to%20Nepal%20today.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20sent%20my%20daughter%20for%20higher%20studies%2C%20trusting%20that%20she%20would%20be%20safe.%20What%20happened%20here%20is%20unacceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20her%20father%2C%20Sunil%20Lamsal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudents%20Manhandled%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Nepalese%20students%20protested%2C%20KIIT%20University%20--%20founded%20and%20run%20by%20veteran%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20leader%20and%20former%20MP%20Achyuta%20Samanta%20--%20instead%20of%20engaging%20with%20the%20students%2C%20responded%20with%20force.%20Security%20personnel%2C%20along%20with%20senior%20university%20officials%2C%20allegedly%20manhandled%20protesting%20students%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20violent%20crackdown%20that%20was%20caught%20on%20camera.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%20showed%20students%20being%20physically%20assaulted%20and%20subjected%20to%20verbal%20abuse.%20In%20one%20of%20those%20videos%2C%20two%20senior%20university%20officials%20were%20also%20seen%20making%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20Nepal%2C%20with%20one%20of%20them%20claiming%20that%20the%20country's%20GDP%20is%20lower%20than%20KIIT's%20budget%20for%20the%20roughly%2040%2C000%20students%20that%20the%20university%20caters%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Odisha%3A%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjHgpcuG1h1%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjHgpcuG1h1%3C%2Fa%3E%20third-year%20girl%20student%20from%20Nepal%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20KIIT%20University%20(Kalinga%20Institute%20of%20Industrial%20Technology)%20hostel%20in%20Bhubaneswar%20on%2016th%20February.%20As%20per%20a%20notice%20issued%20by%20the%20University%2C%20the%20institute%20is%20hence%20closed%20sine%20die%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FvVfgY140up%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FvVfgY140up%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1891389801997431144%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2017%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20continued%20overnight.%20Then%20the%20unexpected%20happened.%20With%20only%20days%20left%20for%20exams%2C%20all%20the%20Nepalese%20students%20were%20told%20to%20leave%20the%20university%20premises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20University%20is%20closed%20Sine%20Die%20for%20all%20the%20International%20students%20from%20Nepal.%20They%20are%20hereby%20directed%20to%20vacate%20the%20university%20campus%20immediately%20today%20on%2017th%20February%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20university%20statement%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20were%20put%20on%20university%20buses%20and%20were%20sent%20packing%20to%20the%20railway%20station%20in%20Cuttack%20to%20fend%20for%20themselves.%20%26quot%3BThey%20(KIIT)%20didn't%20say%20anything%2C%20they%20just%20asked%20us%20to%20leave%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20Nepalese%20student.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOdisha%20Government%20Steps%20In%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Odisha%20government%20on%20Tuesday%20formed%20a%20three-member%20fact-finding%20committee%20to%20investigate%20both%20the%20circumstances%20of%20Prakriti's%20death%20and%20the%20university's%20handling%20of%20student%20protests.%20The%20panel%20is%20led%20by%20the%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%20(Home)%2C%20with%20members%20from%20the%20Higher%20Education%20and%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Higher%20Education%20Minister%20Suryabanshi%20Suraj%20admitted%20that%20KIIT%20authorities%20had%20failed%20to%20inform%20the%20government%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20including%20the%20forced%20eviction%20of%20foreign%20students.%20%26quot%3BThe%20institution%20has%20been%20placed%20under%20notice%2C%20and%20appropriate%20legal%20and%20administrative%20action%20shall%20follow%20based%20on%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20fact-finding%20committee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Suraj%20questioned%20why%20Nepalese%20students%20were%20de-boarded%20at%20Cuttack%20railway%20station%20and%20why%20the%20state%20government%20was%20kept%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20the%20unfolding%20crisis.%20He%20said%20that%20while%20around%20100%20Nepalese%20students%20remain%20on%20campus%2C%20nearly%20800%20others%20have%20left%20for%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EArrests%20and%20Legal%20Action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncluding%20Advik%2C%20the%20Odisha%20Police%20have%20made%20six%20arrests%20in%20connection%20with%20both%20the%20student's%20death%20and%20the%20violence%20against%20protesters.%20Among%20those%20detained%20are%20three%20senior%20university%20officials-Director%20General%20(HR)%20Sibananda%20Mishra%2C%20Director%20(Administration)%20Pratap%20Kumar%20Chamupaty%2C%20and%20Director%20of%20Hostels%20Sudhir%20Kumar%20Rath.%20Two%20security%20guards%2C%20Jogendra%20Behera%20and%20Ramakanta%20Nayak%2C%20were%20also%20arrested%20for%20their%20role%20in%20the%20violent%20crackdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fdna4jr5o_kiit-arrests_625x300_18_February_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20separate%20cases%20have%20been%20filed.%20The%20first%20concerns%20the%20suicide%20and%20was%20registered%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20from%20Prakriti's%20cousin.%20The%20second%20was%20initiated%20by%20the%20police%2C%20following%20viral%20videos%20of%20security%20personnel%20assaulting%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EApologies%20and%20Diplomatic%20Fallout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20KIIT%20faculty%20member%2C%20Manjusha%20Pandey%2C%20was%20heard%20claiming%20in%20the%20viral%20videos%20that%20KIIT%20%26quot%3Bfeeds%20and%20educates%20over%2040%2C000%20students%20for%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20amount%20she%20suggested%20was%20equivalent%20to%20Nepal's%20national%20budget.%20Another%20staff%20member%2C%20Jayanti%20Nath%2C%20was%20recorded%20shouting%20similar%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Ms%20Pandey%20and%20Ms%20Nath%20later%20issued%20public%20apologies.%20%26quot%3BMy%20statements%20were%20made%20in%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Pandey%20said%20in%20a%20video%20message.%20%26quot%3BIf%20my%20words%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20any%20Nepalese%20students%20or%20people%20of%20Nepal%2C%20I%20sincerely%20apologise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22qme%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMEAIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MEAIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPM_nepal_%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40PM_nepal_%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrSJaishankar%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40DrSJaishankar%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPMOIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40PMOIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMofaNepal%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MofaNepal%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndiaInNepal%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40IndiaInNepal%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEONIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40EONIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzPsRL0wNm8%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzPsRL0wNm8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jayanti%20Nath%20(%40JayantiNath6)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJayantiNath6%2Fstatus%2F1891784422451478551%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2018%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKIIT%20also%20issued%20an%20apology%20and%20removed%20two%20of%20its%20officials%20from%20service%2C%20though%20it%20did%20not%20name%20them.%20The%20institute%20urged%20Nepalese%20students%20to%20return%20to%20their%20hostels%20and%20resume%20their%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nepalese%20government%2C%20however%2C%20has%20not%20taken%20the%20issue%20lightly.%20In%20a%20strongly%20worded%20statement%2C%20it%20warned%20that%20it%20might%20suspend%20issuing%20No%20Objection%20Certificates%20(NOCs)%20for%20students%20seeking%20admission%20to%20universities%20in%20Odisha%20if%20the%20matter%20was%20not%20resolved%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bjustifiable%20and%20legal%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENepalese%20Prime%20Minister%20KP%20Sharma%20Oli%20personally%20intervened%2C%20stating%20that%20his%20government%20was%20handling%20the%20matter%20through%20diplomatic%20channels.%20%26quot%3BOur%20Embassy%20in%20New%20Delhi%20has%20dispatched%20officers%20to%20counsel%20affected%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nepalese%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20called%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bunimaginable%26quot%3B%20and%20assured%20that%20it%20was%20in%20continuous%20contact%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20KIIT%20authorities.%20The%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Kathmandu%20also%20pledged%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20Nepalese%20students%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Fallout%20In%20Odisha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20quickly%20turned%20into%20a%20political%20flashpoint%20in%20Odisha.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20demanded%20a%20judicial%20inquiry%2C%20while%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20-%20which%20came%20to%20power%20in%20Odisha%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20history%20after%20their%20shock%20win%20over%20the%20Naveen%20Patnaik-led%20BJD%20in%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20last%20year%20-%20%C2%A0has%20called%20for%20the%20arrest%20of%20KIIT%20founder%20Achyuta%20Samanta.%20The%20BJD%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20blamed%20the%20incident%20on%20deteriorating%20law%20and%20order%20under%20the%20BJP-led%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20was%20also%20raised%20in%20the%20Odisha%20Assembly%2C%20with%20MLAs%20across%20party%20lines%20condemning%20the%20incident.%20%26quot%3BThe%20developments%20at%20KIIT%20have%20brought%20a%20bad%20name%20to%20the%20state%2C%20and%20this%20cannot%20be%20tolerated%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Congress%20MLA%20said%20during%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739953800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fjibios5_prakriti-lamsal-advik-shrivastava-kiit-_625x300_19_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprakriti-lamsal-advik-shrivastava-odisha-nepal-students-body-an-audio-file-how-chaos-unfolded-at-kiit-university-7743779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20university%20in%20Odisha%20was%20celebrating%20its%20three-day%20annual%20fest%2C%20a%20student's%20body%20was%20discovered%20in%20her%20hostel%20room.%20Within%20hours%2C%20the%20discovery%20led%20to%20embassy-level%20talks%20between%20two%20countries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprakriti-lamsal-advik-shrivastava-odisha-nepal-students-body-an-audio-file-how-chaos-unfolded-at-kiit-university-7743779%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Cops%20Detained%20While%20Probing%20Fraud%20In%20UP%2C%20Freed%20After%20They%20Apologised%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20twiste