nai%3A%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Deputy%20CM%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B...We%20are%20not%20playing%20divisive%20politics.%20The%20Union%20Government%2C%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20force%20Hindi%20on%20us...Please%20don't%20impose%203-language%20policy.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fk42k1KFO1X%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fk42k1KFO1X%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1891388307222737327%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2017%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20warned%20the%20Tamil%20people%20against%20the%20three-language%20formula%20or%20accepting%20Hindi%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BDharmendra%20Pradhan%20asks%2C%20'why%20is%20Tamil%20Nadu%20alone%20opposing%20this%20while%20all%20other%20states%20have%20accepted%3F'%20There%20is%20a%20reason...%20several%20states%20that%20accepted%20Hindi%20stand%20to%20lose%20their%20mother%20tongues...%20Bhojpuri%2C%20Bihari%2C%20Haryanvi%20have%20nearly%20died%20because%20of%20infiltration%20by%20Hindi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Certain%20Conditions%20To%20Be%20Met'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-language%20policy%20is%20a%20long-standing%20flashpoint%20between%20southern%20states%20and%20the%20centre%2C%20and%20that%20animosity%20has%20increased%20since%20a%20new%20Education%20Policy%20was%20announced%20five%20years%20ago%3B%20as%20part%20of%20a%20proposed%20revamp%2C%20under%20the%20NEP%20students%20must%20learn%20three%20languages%2C%20one%20of%20which%20will%20be%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20flashpoint%20seemed%20evident%20in%20Mr%20Pradhan's%20comments%20in%20Varanasi%20last%20week.%20He%20accused%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20of%20not%20imposing%20the%20policy%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20of%20political%20interests%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20centre%20is%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20policy%2C%20to%20which%20%26quot%3B...%20there%20are%20certain%20conditions%20to%20be%20met%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20amid%20Tamil%20Nadu%20fury%20over%20Mr%20Pradhan's%20comment%2C%20his%20colleague%2C%20junior%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20L%20Murugan%2C%20who%20is%20from%20the%20southern%20state%2C%20said%20the%20Education%20Minister%20had%20attached%20no%20conditions%20to%20grants%20from%20the%20centre%2C%20and%20slammed%20the%20DMK%20for%20politicising%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%203-Language%20Campaign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20stepped%20up%20its%20three-language%20push%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20will%20vote%20in%20an%20Assembly%20election%20next%20year.%20The%20saffron%20party%20will%20launch%20a%20campaign%20from%20March%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-to-launch-campaign-on-3-language-policy-from-march-1-in-tamil-nadu-7738613%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP%20To%20Launch%20Campaign%20On%203-Language%20Policy%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20push%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20its%20ongoing%20scramble%20for%20a%20foothold%20in%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20political%20landscape.%20The%20party%20has%20historically%20never%20managed%20to%20win%20over%20Tamil%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%20it%20contested%20all%20234%20seats%20but%20won%20zero.%20It%20set%20its%20sights%20lower%20in%202021%2C%20contesting%20just%2020%2C%20but%20managing%20to%20win%20four.%20Its%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20record%20is%20worse%20-%20zero%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20and%202024%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20campaign%20launch%20and%20the%202026%20election%2C%20the%20party's%20state%20unit%20chief%2C%20K%20Annamalai%2C%20has%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20DMK%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20sticking%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Boutdated%2