n%20any%20decisions%20involving%20his%20companies%2C%20which%20the%20South%20African-born%20billionaire%20seconded%20saying%20his%20primary%20role%20was%20to%20provide%20technological%20support%20to%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Musk's%20Power%20In%20Trump%20Administration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20told%20Sean%20Hannity%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bhasn't%20asked%20the%20president%20for%20anything%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20seeking%20to%20reassure%20listeners%20that%20he%20would%20recuse%20himself%20from%20any%20political%20decisions%20that%20involved%20his%20companies.%20Musk's%20companies%2C%20especially%20SpaceX%20hold%20many%20lucrative%20government%20contracts%20and%20work%20directly%20with%20the%20US%20space%20agency%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20also%20reiterated%20that%20Musk%20wouldn't%20be%20involved%20in%20any%20decision-making%20saying%20he%20not%20allow%20him%20to%20work%20on%20government%20projects%20that%20conflicted%20with%20his%20work%20for%20his%20private%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20those%20worried%20about%20his%20power%20as%20an%20unelected%20advisor%20to%20the%20president%20should%20be%20more%20concerned%20about%20the%20thousands%20of%20unelected%20federal%20employees%20in%20the%20government's%20civilian%20workforce.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20bureaucracy%20is%20fighting%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%20and%20preventing%20the%20president%20from%20implementing%20what%20the%20people%20want%2C%20then%20what%20we%20live%20in%20is%20a%20bureaucracy%2C%20not%20a%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWearing%20a%20t-shirt%20that%20read%20%26quot%3Btech%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20billionaire%20stressed%20that%20his%20primary%20role%20was%20to%20provide%20technological%20support%20to%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Role%20Of%20DOGE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20praised%20Musk's%20efficiency%20in%20executing%20executive%20orders%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20gets%20the%20executive%20order%20done.%20There%20used%20to%20be%20signed%20executive%20orders%2C%20but%20no%20work%20got%20done.%20He%20and%20his%20genius%20team%20make%20sure%20they%20are%20executed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20also%20talked%20about%20his%20so-called%20%26quot%3BDepartment%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%26quot%3B%20(%26quot%3BDOGE%26quot%3B)%20and%20said%20that%20with%20it%20the%20Trump%20administration%20aims%20%26quot%3Bto%20try%20to%20get%20a%20trillion%20dollars%20out%20of%20the%20deficit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he's%20going%20to%20find%20a%20trillion%20dollars%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20seconded%2C%20saying%20he%20believed%20it%20would%20only%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20shortage%20of%20fraud%2C%20waste%20and%20abuse%20really%20in%20government%20spending.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20reassured%20voters%20saying%20social%20security%20would%20not%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20cuts%2C%20as%20he%20has%20often%20repeated%2C%20and%20that%20abolishing%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20would%20send%20school%20control%20back%20to%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSocial%20Security%20won't%20be%20touched%2C%20other%20than%20fraud%20or%20something%20-%20we're%20going%20to%20find%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20strengthened%20-%20but%20won't%20be%20touched%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BMedicare%2C%20Medicaid%2C%20none%20of%20that%20stuff%20is%20going%20to%20be%20...%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20touchable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20X%20Lawsuit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHannity%20also%20asked%20the%20pair%20about%20the%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20X's%2C%20recent%20%2410m%20settlement%20with%20the%20president%2C%20a%20question%20which%20was%20dismissed%20by%20both%20Trump%20and%20Musk%20as%20unimportant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20left%20it%20up%20to%20the%20lawyers%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20very%20low%20...%20I%20was%20looking%20to%20get%20much%20more%20money%20than%20that%2C%20so%20you%20gave%20him%20a%20discount%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Assassination%20Attempt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHannity%20noted%20that%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20was%20made%20on%20the%20Republican%20candidate%20Trump's%20life%20the%20day%20Musk%20endorsed%20him%20for%20the%20President.%20The%20Tesla%20CEO%20acknowledged%20that%20and%20praised%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bbravery%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20face%20of%20threat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20--%20this%20is%20how%20you%20know%20someone's%20true%20character%20because%20everyone%20can%20say%20they're%20brave%2C%20but%20the%20president%20was%20actually%20shot.%20%C2%A0Okay%3F%20%C2%A0Courage%20under%20fire.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BFight%2C%20fight%2C%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20blood%20streaming%20down%20the%20face.%20%C2%A0That's%20true%20courage.%20%C2%A0You%20can't%20fake%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739943660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fdbb3nu8o_trump-musk-_625x300_19_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-gets-orders-executed-donald-trump-praises-elon-musk-in-1st-interview-together-7743150%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20billionaire%20ally%20Elon%20Musk%20sat%20down%20for%20their%20first%20joint%20interview%20with%20Fox%20News's%20Sean%20Hannity%20and%20discussed%20various%20topics%20including%20the%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20CEO's%20role%20as%20an%20advisor%20to%20the%20Republican.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-gets-orders-executed-donald-trump-praises-elon-musk-in-1st-interview-together-7743150%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A