A%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGyanesh%20Kumar%2C%20who%20was%20named%20as%20an%20Election%20Commissioner%20last%20year%2C%20has%20been%20appointed%20the%20next%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20of%20India%2C%20replacing%20the%20outgoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar-demits-office-7739148%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajiv%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Mr%20Kumar%20will%20oversee%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20Bihar%20Assembly%20election%20later%20this%20year%20and%20the%20polls%20in%20Bengal%2C%20Assam%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20next%20year.%20He%20took%20charge%20as%20the%20new%20poll%20chief%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanesh-kumar-appointed-new-chief-election-commissioner-7733534%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKumar%3C%2Fa%3E's%20appointment%20came%20in%20a%20late-night%20development%20on%20Monday%2C%20within%20hours%20after%20a%20meeting%20of%20a%20three-member%20panel%20consisting%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20(LoP)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmidnight-decision-of-pm-home-minister-disrespectful-rahul-gandhis-dissent-note-over-top-election-officers-appointment-7736876%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20sparked%20a%20row%20as%20Mr%20Gandhi%20did%20not%20approve%20of%20the%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERow%20on%20Gyanesh%20Kumar's%20appointment%20explained%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20Mr%20Kumar%20as%20the%20poll%20chief%20was%20done%20based%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-election-commissioner-gyanesh-kumar-who-is-gyanesh-kumar-likely-to-be-new-chief-election-commissioner-7731982%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChief%20Election%20Commissioner%3C%2Fa%3Es%20and%20Election%20Commissioners%20(ECs)%20under%20the%202023%20law.%20According%20to%20these%20rules%2C%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioners%20and%20Election%20Commissioners%20will%20be%20appointed%20by%20the%20President%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20a%20selection%20committee%20consisting%20of%20PM%20Modi%20as%20the%20Chairperson%2C%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20nominated%20by%20the%20PM%20-%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20law%20was%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20the%20three-member%20panel%20allowed%20the%20Centre%20a%20dominant%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20was%20set%20to%20take%20up%20a%20hearing%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bpriority%20basis%26quot%3B%20on%20February%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20this%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20present%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20had%20opposed%20Mr%20Kumar's%20appointment%20and%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20postpone%20it.%20However%2C%20the%20Centre%20planned%20to%20press%20on%20regardless%2C%20saying%20that%20halting%20the%20process%20would%20mean%20leaving%20the%20key%20post%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20Kumar's%20appointment%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20gave%20a%20dissent%20note%20saying%20the%20meeting%20was%20meaningless%20as%20the%20new%20law%20has%20been%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20committee%20to%20select%20the%20next%20(Chief)%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20I%20presented%20a%20dissent%20note%20to%20the%20PM%20and%20HM%20that%20stated%3A%20'The%20most%20fundamental%20aspect%20of%20an%20independent%20Election%20Commission...%20free%20from%20executive%20interference...%20is%20the%20process%20of%20choosing%20the%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner.%20By%20violating%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20and%20removing%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20from%20the%20committee%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20exacerbated%20the%20concerns%20of%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20voters%20over%20the%20integrity%20of%20our%20electoral%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20LoP%2C%20it%20is%20my%20duty%20to%20uphold%20the%20ideals%20of%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20and%20the%20founding%20leaders%20of%20our%20nation%20and%20hold%20the%20government%20to%20account.%20It%20is%20both%20disrespectful%20and%20discourteous%20for%20the%20PM%20and%20HM%20to%20have%20made%20a%20midnight%20decision%20to%20select%20the%20new%20CEC%2C%20when%20the%20very%20composition%20of%20the%20committee%20and%20the%20process%20is%20being%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20is%20due%20to%20be%20heard%20in%20less%20than%20forty-eight%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Saket%20Gokhale%20also%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20calling%20Mr%20Shah%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20new%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongratulations%20to%20Sh%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20becoming%20India's%20new%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner.%20The%20nation%20is%20confident%20that%20under%20your%20able%20leadership%2C%20the%20goal%20of%20reducing%20ECI%20to%20a%20wing%20of%20BJP%20will%20be%20successfully%20achieved%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20not%20succeed%20in%20West%20Bengal%20despite%20the%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20is%20a%201988-batch%20IAS%20officer%20from%20the%20Kerala%20cadre.%20He%20is%20the%20senior%20of%20the%20two%20commissioners%20on%20the%20three-member%20panel%20that%20was%20led%20by%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20till%20he%20demitted%20office.%20The%20other%20commissioner%20on%20the%20panel%20is%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%2C%20an%20officer%20from%20the%20Uttarakhand%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20earlier%20and%20had%20helped%20draft%20the%20bill%20that%20scrapped%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20August%202019%20and%20split%20the%20former%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20served%20as%20the%20Joint%20Secretary%20(Kashmir%20Division)%20and%20the%20Additional%20Secretary%20in%20the%20Home%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739939700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fng8di7vo_gynaesh-kumar_625x300_19_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-explainer-why-gyanesh-kumars-appointment-as-poll-chief-sparked-row-7743230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gyanesh%20Kumar%2C%20who%20was%20named%20as%20an%20Election%20Commissioner%20last%20year%2C%20has%20been%20appointed%20the%20next%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20of%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-explainer-why-gyanesh-kumars-appointment-as-poll-chief-sparked-row-7743230%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gyanesh%20Kumar%20Takes%20Over%20Ahead%20of%20Top%20Court%20Hearing%20On%20Poll%20Chief%20Selection%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fgyanesh-kumar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGyanesh%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20assumed%20charge%20Wednesday%20morning%20as%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fchief-election-commissioner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChief%20Election%20Commissioner%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20replaces%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20in%20the%20role%20and%20will%20oversee%20the%20conduct%20of%20nearly%20two-dozen%20elections%2C%20state%20and%20presidential%2C%20over%20the%20course%20of%20his%20four-year%20term.%20The%20new%20CEC%20is%20an%20ex-IAS%20officer%20from%20the%20Kerala%20cadre%2C%20and%20earlier%20served%20in%20the%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20under%20current%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Among%20his%20key%20responsibilities%20were%20the%20drafting%20of%20a%20bill%20that%20scrapped%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20remarks%20after%20taking%20charge%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20first%20step%20for%20nation-building%20is%20voting.%20Therefore%2C%20every%20citizen%20of%20India%20who%20has%20completed%2018%20years%20of%20age%20should%20become%20an%20elector%20and%20should%20always%20vote.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20was%2C%20is%2C%20and%20will%20always%20be%20with%20the%20voters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20appointment%20-%20the%20notification%20was%20issued%20late%20last%20night%20-%20was%20made%20amid%20controversy%20after%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Congress%20objected%20to%20his%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20is%20part%20of%20a%20three-member%20panel%20that%20was%20tasked%20with%20picking%20the%20new%20CEC%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20leader%20submitted%20a%20dissent%20note%20instead%2C%20objecting%20to%20Gyanesh%20Kumar's%20nomination%20despite%20a%20challenge%20-%20to%20the%20constitution%20of%20the%20panel%20-%20that%20is%20pending%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanesh-kumar-appointed-new-chief-election-commissioner-7733534%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGyanesh%20Kumar%20Appointed%20New%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20will%20hear%20those%20arguments%20later%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20essence%2C%20the%20contention%20is%20the%20committee%20-%20which%20at%20present%20consists%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20a%20member%20of%20th