Cp%3ERapper%20A%24AP%20Rocky%20was%20found%20not%20guilty%20of%20two%20counts%20of%20felony%20assault%20at%20the%20conclusion%20of%20a%20trial%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20musician%2C%20who%20has%20two%20children%20with%20singer%20Rihanna%2C%20had%20faced%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20in%20prison%20if%20he%20had%20been%20convicted%20of%20the%20alleged%20attack%20on%20a%20former%20friend%20in%20Hollywood%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20commotion%20in%20the%20courtroom%20as%20the%20jury's%20verdict%20was%20read%20out%2C%20with%20the%20Grammy-nominated%20hip%20hop%20star%2C%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20Rakim%20Mayers%2C%20hugging%20people%20in%20relief%20as%20he%20was%20declared%20not%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20weeks-long%20trial%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20Mayers%20had%20shot%20a%20nine-millimeter%20semi-automatic%20weapon%20during%20a%20confrontation%20with%20Terell%20Ephron%2C%20also%20known%20as%20A%24AP%20Relli%2C%20on%20November%206%2C%202021%2C%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Hollywood%2C%20grazing%20Ephron's%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayers%2C%2036%2C%20had%20insisted%20he%20had%20been%20carrying%20only%20a%20harmless%20prop%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20had%20previously%20been%20friends%2C%20and%20had%20both%20been%20part%20of%20A%24AP%2C%20a%20rap%20collective%20from%20New%20York%2C%20but%20had%20fallen%20out%20because%20other%20members%20of%20the%20group%20felt%20Mayers'%20commercial%20success%20had%20made%20him%20arrogant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEphron%20told%20the%20jury%20he%20had%20been%20lured%20to%20a%20parking%20garage%20for%20an%20encounter%20that%20was%20partially%20caught%20on%20grainy%20surveillance%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20after%20the%20two%20exchanged%20words%2C%20Mayers%20pulled%20a%20gun%20from%20his%20waistband%2C%20put%20it%20toward%20Relli's%20stomach%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'll%20kill%20you%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEphron%20said%20two%20bu