ation%2C%20Narendra%20Singh%20Mehra%2C%2066%2C%20is%20driven%20by%20a%20singular%20belief%20%E2%80%94%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F390877%2Funnao-uttarpradesh-peanut-farmers-nutty-village-agriculture-startup-tiss%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efarmers%20deserve%20their%20due%20recognition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20deserve%20to%20eat%20pure%2C%20healthy%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20developing%20a%20new%20variety%20of%20wheat%20that%20thrives%20in%20different%20conditions%20to%20regenerating%20organic%20sugarcane%20farming%2C%20Mehra%20has%20spent%20decades%20experimenting%2C%20learning%2C%20and%20perfecting%20agricultural%20practices.%20With%20his%20ingenious%20methods%20of%20farming%2C%20he%20has%20shown%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20to%20grow%20food%20that%20nourishes%20both%20the%20land%20and%20the%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20ask%20a%20child%20to%20draw%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20farmer%2C%20he%20will%20draw%20one%20that%20depicts%20the%20hardships%20of%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20life.%20I%20hope%20to%20change%20that%20so%20the%20image%20of%20a%20farmer%20is%20that%20of%20a%20proud%20man%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20seeds%20of%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarendra%20Singh%20Mehra%20was%20born%20in%201959%2C%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Devla%20Malla%2C%20Nainital.%20Growing%20up%20in%20a%20family%20where%20agriculture%20was%20the%20way%20of%20life%2C%20he%20was%20very%20attached%20to%20his%20land%20and%20the%20farming%20community.%20His%20family%2C%20however%2C%20wanted%20him%20to%20get%20an%20education%20and%20settle%20in%20a%20big%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20do%20not%20want%20their%20children%20to%20become%20farmers.%20The%20condition%20of%20farmers%20is%20such%20that%20leaving%20your%20homeland%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20ancestral%20and%20you%20are%20attached%20to%20it%2C%20is%20the%20norm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-7_11zon-1739503958.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Narendra%20Singh%20Mehra%20was%20concerned%20with%20the%20growing%20trend%20of%20farmers%20switching%20to%20crops%20like%20soybeans%20and%20tomatoes%20from%20wheat%20and%20other%20grain%20crops%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-7_11zon-1739503958.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-7_11zon-1739503958-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-7_11zon-1739503958-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-7_11zon-1739503958-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-7_11zon-1739503958-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-406030%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Singh%20Mehra%20was%20concerned%20with%20the%20growing%20trend%20of%20farmers%20switching%20to%20crops%20like%20soybeans%20and%20tomatoes%20from%20wheat%20and%20other%20grain%20crops%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20he%20did.%20By%201984%2C%20Mehra%20had%20studied%20