0Mars%2C%20the%20Marianas%20Mars%2C%20the%20Marshall%20Mars%2C%20the%20firefighting%20variant%20of%20the%20Hawaii%20Mars%2C%20and%20the%20Caroline%20Mars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20fleet%20has%20been%20scrapped%2C%20lost%2C%20or%20destroyed%20over%20the%20last%20eight%20decades%2C%20the%20second%20Hawaii%20Mars%20and%20the%20Philippine%20Mars%20survived%20to%20this%20day.%20The%20Hawaii%20Mars%20was%20donated%20to%20the%20British%20Columbia%20Aviation%20Museum%20in%20Canada%2C%20and%20the%20Philippine%20Mars%20will%20make%20its%20final%20home%20at%20the%20Pima%20Air%20and%20Space%20in%20Tucson%2C%20Arizona.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Navy's%20largest%20World%20War%20II-era%20aircraft%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221014%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20Navy%20sailor%20assisted%20a%20passenger%20as%20she%20disembarked%20the%20Philippine%20Mars.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ae505deb4be2fff9a498de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20Navy%20sailor%20assisted%20a%20passenger%20as%20she%20disembarked%20the%20Philippine%20Mars.%3Cp%3ETed%20Huggins%2FNaval%20History%20and%20Heritage%20Command%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mars%20flying%20boats%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-largest-floatplane-takes-first-flight-in-china-spruce-goose-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20world's%20largest%20operational%20seaplanes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Navy's%20largest%20WWII-era%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20measured%20nearly%20120%20feet%20in%20length%20and%20200%20feet%20in%20wingspan%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20the%20size%20of%20a%20modern-day%20Boeing%20commercial%20airplane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20flying%20boats%20were%20reconfigured%20from%20patrol%20boats%20to%20cargo%20planes%2C%20the%20massive%20flying%20boat%20had%20a%20max%20takeoff%20weight%20of%20over%2085%20tons%20%E2%80%94%20