%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4fa7c7bb3f854015d2e7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225261%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELionel%20BONAVENTURE%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDOGE%20staffer%20Marko%20Elez%20was%20listed%20as%20an%20employee%20on%20xAI's%20internal%20database%20as%20of%20last%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EElez%20resigned%20from%20DOGE%20after%20being%20linked%20to%20controversial%20social%20media%20posts.%20Musk%20promised%20to%20rehire%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EElez%20worked%20for%20X%20and%20SpaceX.%20His%20employment%20at%20xAI%20was%20previously%20unreported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMarko%20Elez%2C%20who%20resigned%20from%20and%20was%20then%20rehired%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recently%20worked%20for%20Elon%20Musk's%20xAI%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElez%20previously%20worked%20as%20an%20engineer%20for%20two%20other%20Musk%20companies%2C%20SpaceX%20and%20X%2C%20according%20to%20an%20archived%20version%20of%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile.%20The%20archived%20profile%20did%20not%20mention%20working%20at%20xAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20xAI%20organization%20chart%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20last%20week%2C%20Elez%20was%20listed%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bactive%26quot%3B%20employee.%20Elez%20began%20working%20at%20the%20AI%20startup%20on%20October%202%2C%202024%2C%20and%20his%20role%20was%20listed%20as%20%26quot%3BX%20Corp%20Partner.%26quot%3B%20(X%20Corp%20is%20the%20name%20of%20the%20company%20that%20owns%20the%20social%20media%20site%20X.)%20He%20was%20placed%20within%20the%20department%20%26quot%3BxAI%20Partner%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20five%20members%2C%20according%20to%20the%20internal%20organization%20chart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20what%20the%20business%20unit%20does.%20xAI%20has%20built%20a%20Grok%20chatbot%20for%20X%20and%20shares%20a%20data%20center%20in%20Atlanta%20with%20the%20social%20media%20company%2C%20according%20to%20public%20records%20viewed%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElez%20sat%20two%20levels%20below%20cofounder%20Igor%20Babuschkin%20on%20the%20xAI%20org%20chart.%20Babuschkin%20reports%20directly%20to%20Musk%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20org%20chart%20does%20not%20say%20the%20exact%20employment%20status%20of%20Elez%20or%20any%20xAI%20employees%2C%20only%20that%20he%20was%20active%20in%20the%20company.%20It's%20unclear%20how%20recently%20xAI%20has%20updated%20its%20org%20chart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExAI%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20Elez's%20employment%20status%20at%20the%20company.%20Within%20four%20days%20after%20BI%20contacted%20the%20company%20for%20comment%2C%20Elez's%20xAI%20email%20account%20stopped%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20emails%20were%20sent%20to%20Elez's%20xAI%20address%20on%20February%2014%2C%20they%20were%20delivered.%20A%20follow-up%20email%20sent%20on%20Tuesday%20bounced%20back%20with%20the%20message%20%26quot%3Bthe%20email%20account%20that%20you%20tried%20to%20reach%20is%20inactive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2025-year-old%20Elez%20made%20headlines%20earlier%20this%20month%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fdoge-staffer-resigns-over-racist-posts-d9f11a93%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20Elez's%20since-deleted%20social%20media%20account%20with%20inflammatory%20posts%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20racist%20before%20it%20was%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElez%20resigned%20from%20his%20government%20role%20after%20the%20Journal%20contacted%20government%20officials%20for%20comment.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20two%20Musk%20recruits%20who%20had%20worked%20within%20the%20US%20Treasury%20Department.%20DOGE's%20access%20to%20the%20central%20Treasury%20payment%20has%20sparked%20a%20lawsuit%20fr