20prominent%2C%20but%20not%20in%20a%20shouty%20way.%20According%20to%20Drop%2C%20the%206XX's%20bass%20can%20best%20be%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bnatural%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsatisfying%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20we%20agree%20with.%20It%20may%20not%20be%20what%20you're%20used%20to%2C%20but%20it's%20adequate.%20The%20treble%20is%20similarly%20smooth%20and%20clear.%20Thus%20these%20headphones%20offer%20a%20very%20easy%2C%20pleasant%20aural%20experience%20throughout%20long%20listening%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241aff699-84ca-453f-bf10-54173102b93a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Audio%20performance%5C%22%3EThe%20HD%206XX's%20open-back%20design%20enables%20excellent%20timbre%2C%20texture%2C%20and%20imaging%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drop%206XX%20headphones%20compared%20to%20Sennheiser's%20closed-back%20620S%20headphones.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4ed3b6630eb10385ce937%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20open-back%20HD%206XX%20headphones%20(left)%20offer%20a%20more%20spacious%20sound%20than%20the%20closed-back%20HD%20620S%20(right).%3Cp%3EScott%20Tharler%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20audio%20arena%2C%20timbre%20(pronounced%20like%20%26quot%3Btamber%26quot%3B)%20refers%20to%20how%20natural%20and%20unprocessed%20vocals%20and%20instruments%20sound.%20As%20a%20rule%2C%20open-back%20headphones%20like%20the%20HD%206XX%2C%20which%20let%20sound%20in%20and%20out%20of%20their%20open%20or%20vented%20ear%20cups%2C%20tend%20to%20produce%20more%20natural%20audio%20than%20closed-back%20models%2C%20which%20have%20sealed%20ear%20cups%20that%20prevent%20sound%20from%20getting%20out.%20For%20example%2C%20Sennheiser's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74704-20%26h%3D23b63f2968dbc5072fceaaab1888c6e701937e9b28e680423783c14cd2be756e%26postID%3D67b4b2325794bed738617a65%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fdrop-sennheiser-hd-6xx-headphones-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSennheiser-620S-Closed-Back-Headphones-Speaker-Like%252Fdp%252FB0D38B6XWR%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHD%20620S%3C%2Fa%3E%20sound%20great%20for%20closed-back%20headphones%2C%20but%20they%20can't%20compete%20in%20timbre%20with%20the%20airiness%20and%20spaciousness%20of%20the%20HD%206XX's%20open-back%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETexture%20is%20another%20underrated%20aspect%20of%20audio.%20With%20other%20headphones%2C%20the%20sub-bass%20range%20can%20come%20off%20as%20growly%20and%20sloppy%2C%20the%20mid-bass%20as%20overly%20punchy%20and%20thumpy%2C%20the%20mids%20as%20lacking%20and%20anemic%2C%20and%20the%20treble%20as%20sparkly%20and%20shouty.%20Any%20combination%20of%20these%20traits%20creates%20a%20jagged%20mess.%20But%20with%20the%206XX%2C%20music%20comes%20through%20clear%20and%20steady%20across%20the%20board.%20The%20bass%20is%20present%20but%20contained%2C%20mids%20are%20tastefully%20pronounced%2C%20and%20the%20treble%20is%20warm%20and%20bright.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20that%20last%20aspect%2C%20certain%20tracks%20that%20presented%20a%20challenge%20on%20other%20headphones%20(coming%20off%20as%20sizzling%20and%20sibilant)%20were%20nice%20and%20smooth%20on%20the%206XX.%20Specifically%2C%20in%20the%20live%20version%20of%20%26quot%3BHotel%20California%2C%26quot%3B%20certain%20phrases%20end%20in%20a%20hissy%20S%20on%20many%20headphones%2C%20but%20not%20the%206XX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImaging%20is%20another%20way%20to%20describe%20how%20headphones%20sound%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20instrument%20separation.%20If%20you%20were%20listening%20live%20in%20a%20studio%20or%20a%20club%2C%20you'd%20see%20and%20hear%20that%20the%20musicians%20aren't%20literally%20right%20on%20top%20of%20each%20other.%20Each%20artist%20has%20their%20own%20place%20in%20the%20booth%20o