2F67b4cc74eb4be2fff9a4e786%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20took%20a%20beat%20for%20the%20cookies%20made%20with%20egg%20replacer%20to%20turn%20golden.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%2012%20minutes%20in%20the%20oven%2C%20the%20egg-replacer%20finally%20cookies%20fell%20out%20of%20their%20rounded%2C%20scooped%20shapes%20and%20looked%20more%20like%20what%20I%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20another%20five%20minutes%20(for%20a%20total%20of%2017)%20before%20they%20were%20golden%20and%20baked%20through.%20The%20resulting%20cookie%20still%20retained%20a%20lot%20of%20height%20in%20the%20oven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20cookies%20made%20with%20an%20egg%20replacer%20had%20good%20rise%20and%20a%20soft%20center.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cookie%20made%20with%20egg%20replacer%20on%20plate%2C%20scraggly%20edges%20but%20golden%20brown%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4d266eb4be2fff9a4e8ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20batch%20of%20cookies%20I%20made%20with%20egg%20replacer%20looked%20golden%20brown.%20%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bottoms%20of%20the%20cookies%20were%20dark%20golden%20and%20very%20crispy%2C%20and%20the%20top%20had%20some%20crispiness%20as%20well.%20The%20center%20was%20gooey%20and%20soft%2C%20just%20shy%20of%20being%20underbaked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20flavor%2C%20these%20tasted%20very%20close%20to%20the%20original%20recipe%20with%20egg%2C%20but%20I%20did%20get%20an%20extra%20hint%20of%20starch%20that%20had%20a%20very%20slight%20floury%20taste.%20That%20could%20be%20because%20the%20egg%20replacer%20contains%20potato%20starch%2C%20baking%20soda%2C%20tapioca%20flour%2C%20and%20psyllium%20husk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20this%20flavor%20would%20be%20noticeable%20to%20someone%20who%20wasn't%20closely%20examining%20the%20cookie%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EApplesauce%20could%20bind%20and%20emulsify%20in%20the%20recipe.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cookies%20ingredients%20laid%20out%20with%20cup%20of%20applesauce%2C%20butter%2C%20chocolate%20chips%2C%20vanilla%2C%20flour%2C%20sugars%2C%20butter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4cd386630eb10385ce3d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20time%2C%20I%20used%20applesauce%20instead%20of%20egg%20in%20my%20cookie%20recipe.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fegg-substitute%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eegg-replacement%20chart%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20applesauce%20would%20be%20helpful%20for%20binding%20the%20dough%20and%20thickening%20the%20cookies%2C%20but%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20too%20great%20for%20leavening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20flaxseed%20was%20good%20for%20binding%20only%2C%20while%20egg%20replacer%20was%20ideal%20for%20binding%2C%20emulsifying%2C%20and%20leavening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20alternatives%20I%20tried%2C%20applesauce%20felt%20especially%20accessible%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20since%20I%20typically%20keep%20it%20on%20hand%20anyway%2C%20and%20it%20has%20many%20uses%20(including%20being%20eaten%20on%20its%20own).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20experiment%2C%20I%20bought%20the%20cheapest%20option%20at%20my%20local%20grocery%20store%3A%20six%20small%20cups%20of%20applesauce%20for%20%243.%20I%20used%201%2F4%20cup%20of%20applesauce%20(nearly%20all%20of%20one%20single-serving%20cup)%20to%20replace%20one%20egg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20dough%20was%20sticky%20and%20produced%20fewer%20cookies%20than%20usual.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cookie%20dough%20made%20using%20applesauce%20in%20metal%20bowl%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4cd89eb4be2fff9a4e7c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20applesauce%20seemed%20to%20make%20my%20dough%20more%20dense%20and%20sticky.%20%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dough%20certainly%20smelled%20good%2C%20but%20the%20applesauce%20made%20it%20dense%20and%20sticky.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cookie%20scoop%20I%20used%20packed%20the%20dense%20dough%20in%20so%20much%20that%20this%20batch%20made%20only%2011%20cookies%20instead%20of%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20applesauce%20cookies%20looked%20thick%20and%20pale.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20chip%20cookies%20made%20with%20applesauce%20that%20seem%20flat%2C%20pale%20on%20top%20with%20golden%20edges%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4cdba7bb3f854015d25b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cookies%20I%20made%20using%20applesauce%20instead%20of%20egg%20didn't%20look%20quite%20right%20as%20they%20baked.%20%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20cookies%20took%20about%2019%20minutes%20to%20bake%2C%20as%20they%20were%20staying%20too%20soft%20on%20top%20and%20looked%20pale%20for%20longer%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20they'd%20cooled%2C%20they%20looked%20very%20thick%20but%20much%20lighter%20in%20color%20than%20my%20other%20batches.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20applesauce%20made%20for%20some%20very%20chewy%20cookies.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cookie%20made%20using%20applesauce%20on%20a%20plate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4cdd76630eb10385ce3f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20applesauce%20made%20these%20cookies%20chewier.%20%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20had%20a%20good%20flavor%20and%20tasted%20like%20standard%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies%2C%20with%20no%20hint%20of%20apple%20at%20all.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20perhaps%20because%20of%20the%20added%20sugar%20in%20applesauce%2C%20they%20were%20very%20chewy%20and%20tougher%20than%20the%20others%20I%20baked.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20weren't%20unpleasant%20to%20eat%20by%20any%20means%2C%20but%20the%20texture%20just%20wasn't%20as%20good%20as%20the%20other%20batches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPlain%20yogurt%20is%20a%20staple%20in%20my%20house%2C%20and%20the%20cookies%20only%20needed%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20it.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cookie%20ingredients%20including%20vanilla%2C%20flour%2C%20sugars%2C%20butter%2C%20chocolate%20chips%2C%20and%20cup%20of%20yogurt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4d2126630eb10385ce4b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20didn't%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20yogurt%20for%20this%20substitution.%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20plain%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-add-to-smoothies-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyogurt%20for%20smoothies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bowls%2C%20and%20even%20as%20a%20sour-cream%20alternative%2C%20so%20I%20always%20have%20a%20tub%20of%20it%20in%20the%20fridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20test%2C%20I%20used%20a%20scoop%20from%20my%2024-ounce%20tub%20of%202%25%20fat%20plain%20yogurt%20from%20a%20local%20dairy%20producer%20that%20cost%20me%20%247.50.%20However%2C%20a%20small%2C%20single-serving%20cup%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-grocery-store-greek-yogurt-brand-is-best-comparison-2016-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estore-brand%20yogurt%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20work%20for